descriptionMarkdown:
Small starter base to be able to rush bots

60 SPM: Red, Green, Grey, Blue

Notes:
- Be careful to update the red circuits underground belts - it must have 2 colors to work
- Steel is a bottleneck - Improve steel furnaces as soon as you can
- No space production in this blueprint, only the cargo landing pad
- On midgame you can double the size of the furnaces block to consume full ore belts if you want, but it is not really needed
title: Starter Base, Bot Rush + Early Mall
